Income View Instructions 11


1.  Right Click and Duplicate the No IT Exp worksheet

2.  Rename it to Income

3.  Remove the Pills in the Columns and Rows Shelves

4.  Remove _cc.ITEXP% from the Marks Card

 

5.  Right Click and Drag Start Date to Columns and Select Week(Continuous(Green))



6.  Drag _cc.Household Income MEASURE into Rows  and change the Aggregation to Average



7.  Hold Down the CTRL button and drag AVG([_cc.Household Income MEASURE]) from the      Rows shelf to Label.

8. Click Label and select Line Ends



 9.   Drag _cc.Household Income MEASURE AVG into Details
10.  Drag _cc.CountEntireTable TOTAL into Details
11.  Right Click the Y Axis and select Remove Header.
12.   Right Click the X Axis and select Remove Header.



13.   Double Click title. Highlight Missing Field. Select INSERT and select cc.Household Income MEASURE AVG
